-- Huawei Says Motorola Claim It Stole Mobile-Phone Trade Secrets Groundless
-- Pavel Alpeyev
-- 2010-07-21T23:53:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-21/huawei-says-motorola-claim-it-stole-mobile-phone-trade-secrets-groundless.html

          
          
             Huawei Technologies Co. said
Motorola Inc.’s claim that the Chinese company conspired to
steal trade secrets is false.  
 “The complaint is groundless and utterly without merit,”
Huawei said in a statement. “Huawei will vigorously defend
itself against baseless allegations.”  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Pavel Alpeyev in Tokyo at 
 palpeyev@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        